graph TD
    Start[Schema Change Needed] --> Type{Change Type?}

    Type -->|Add Column| ADD[Add Optional Column]
    Type -->|Remove Column| REMOVE[Remove Column]
    Type -->|Modify Type| MODIFY[Modify Data Type]
    Type -->|Rename Column| RENAME[Rename Column]

    ADD --> ADD1{Backward Compatible?}
    ADD1 -->|Yes - Optional| SAFE1[✓ Safe Evolution<br/>Set default=null]
    ADD1 -->|No - Required| UNSAFE1[⚠️ Breaking Change<br/>Backfill required]

    REMOVE --> REMOVE1{Still Queried?}
    REMOVE1 -->|Yes| UNSAFE2[⚠️ Breaking Change<br/>Update queries first]
    REMOVE1 -->|No| SAFE2[✓ Safe to Remove<br/>Archive old data]

    MODIFY --> MODIFY1{Compatible Cast?}
    MODIFY1 -->|Yes - Widening| SAFE3[✓ Safe Evolution<br/>int32 → int64<br/>string → text]
    MODIFY1 -->|No - Narrowing| UNSAFE3[⚠️ Validate Data<br/>Could lose precision]

    RENAME --> RENAME1[⚠️ Breaking Change]
    RENAME1 --> RENAME2[Create Alias/View<br/>Deprecate old name<br/>Migrate gradually]

    SAFE1 --> PROCESS[Evolution Process]
    SAFE2 --> PROCESS
    SAFE3 --> PROCESS

    UNSAFE1 --> REVIEW[Review & Plan]
    UNSAFE2 --> REVIEW
    UNSAFE3 --> REVIEW
    RENAME2 --> REVIEW

    PROCESS --> P1[1. Update Schema Definition]
    P1 --> P2[2. Test with Sample Data]
    P2 --> P3[3. Update Data Catalog]
    P3 --> P4[4. Deploy to Production]
    P4 --> P5[5. Monitor Queries]

    REVIEW --> R1[1. Impact Analysis]
    R1 --> R2[2. Create Migration Plan]
    R2 --> R3[3. Update Dependent Systems]
    R3 --> R4[4. Staged Rollout]
    R4 --> R5[5. Validate & Monitor]

    P5 --> DONE[✓ Schema Updated]
    R5 --> DONE

    style SAFE1 fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style SAFE2 fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style SAFE3 fill:#4CAF50,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style UNSAFE1 fill:#F44336,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style UNSAFE2 fill:#F44336,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style UNSAFE3 fill:#FF9800,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style RENAME1 fill:#F44336,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style DONE fill:#FFD700,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
